":"而家機場無晒人無晒班次<br />\n機管局局無晒收入<br />\n空運量亦都應該會長遠地受影響<br />\n三跑隨時爛尾都唔出奇"},{"pid":"c6b8d48a74eac329827b82c8511eaaa998e3dd40","tid":2151680,"uid":87511,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T14:54:29.000Z","msg":"抵撚死<br />\n上年要入, 唔畀人入<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而家你求我我都唔撚入"},{"pid":"766b13827ff05e5892a777cd6ed9917dff608984","tid":2151680,"uid":200083,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T14:55:17.000Z","msg":"禁制令大法好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ce047fbad2a0382b2e91c9327fcf7c4f1905941","tid":2151680,"uid":83582,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"3b12c9c4333ed08be2155a9fe97f5aa3739ab859","tid":2151680,"uid":113000,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T14:51:27.000Z","msg":"國安法下仲少人黎香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n條三跑超級大笨象"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T14:59:09.000Z","msg":"將來肯定少左外國人經香港轉機, 一陣畀你捉去做人質"},{"pid":"47382156cf1b46f14d403b330d0d98df5f53117a","tid":2151680,"uid":53062,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T15:00:36.000Z","msg":"唔驚，有禁制令，可以禁止商戶唔續租<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}